---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/lameck-5.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/ArticlesPost.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Imaging Uganda/Africa"
  description="From a grassroots WhatsApp community to a leading educational platform bridging the gap between radiology professionals and patients."
  pubDate={new Date('May 23 2026')}
  heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
  <p>
    <strong>Imaging Uganda/Africa</strong> began with a simple mission: to connect local medical imaging professionals, share knowledge, and discuss challenging diagnostic cases. What started as a focused, passionate WhatsApp group has grown into a dynamic educational platform dedicated to advancing radiology across the region.
  </p>

  <p>
    Today, we bridge the gap between healthcare providers, students, and patients. By providing high-quality educational content, detailed radiology case studies, and accessible resources on advanced imaging techniques, we empower professionals to sharpen their diagnostic skills and help patients understand their medical procedures.
  </p>

  <p>
    As our community expands across East Africa and the broader continent, we remain committed to fostering collaboration, improving diagnostic accuracy, and highlighting the latest technological advancements in the field of radiology.
  </p>

  <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef; margin: 3rem 0 2rem 0;" />

  <h2 style="font-size: 26px; color: rgb(0, 0, 139); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Our Founders</h2>
  <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Select a founder below to view their full professional curriculum vitae (CV).</p>
  
  <!-- Founders Grid Layout -->
  <div class="founders-grid">
    <!-- Founder 1 -->
    <a href="/cvs/mwanje-pishon" class="founder-card" title="View CV of Mwanje Pishon">
      <div class="avatar-placeholder">🩻</div>
      <h3>Mwanje Pishon</h3>
      <p class="role">Medical Imaging Technologist (MIT) & Co-Founder</p>
      <p class="bio">Mwanje Pishon is a Ugandan by nationality male gender. I am a registered medical imaging technologist by Allied Health Profession Council-AHPC...</p>
      <span class="cv-link-text">View CV &rarr;</span>
    </a>

    <!-- Founder 2 -->
    <a href="/cvs/lameck" class="founder-card" title="View CV of lameckx">
      <div class="avatar-placeholder">🩺</div>
      <h3>LAMECK</h3>
      <p class="role">Medical Imaging Technologist (MIT) & Co-Founder</p>
      <p class="bio">A God fearing, industrious, highly skilled and reliable Radiographer with leadership and organizational skills. Over 13 years experience in diagno...</p>
      <span class="cv-link-text">View CV &rarr;</span>
    </a>

    <!-- Founder 3 -->
    <a href="/cvs/ssenyonga-henr" class="founder-card" title="View CV of Ssenyonga Henr">
      <div class="avatar-placeholder">🧬</div>
      <h3>Ssenyonga Henry</h3>
      <p class="role">Medical Imaging Technologist (MIT) & Co-Founder</p>
      <p class="bio">Ugandan by nationality male gender. I am a registered medical radiographer. I diagnose using the following imaging modalities; ultras...</p>
      <span class="cv-link-text">View CV &rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .founders-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .founder-card {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
  }
  .founder-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgb(0, 0, 139);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 139, 0.08);
  }
  .avatar-placeholder {
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 139, 0.08);
    color: rgb(0, 0, 139);
    font-size: 28px;
    line-height: 70px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    transition: background 0.2s ease;
  }
  .founder-card:hover .avatar-placeholder {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 139, 0.15);
  }
  .founder-card h3 {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.25rem 0;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: #212529;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .founder-card:hover h3 {
    color: rgb(0, 0, 139);
  }
  .role {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgb(0, 0, 139);
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .founder-card .bio {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }
  .cv-link-text {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: rgb(0, 0, 139);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
</style>
